<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Maintenance — Amethyste Idle</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@600;700&family=Nunito:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #0f0e17;
            --bg-card: #1a1926;
            --amethyst: #8b5cf6;
            --amethyst-glow: #a78bfa;
            --amethyst-dark: #5b21b6;
            --text: #e2e8f0;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -20%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15), transparent),
                radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 100%, rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.12), transparent);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 480px;
        }
        .crystal {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            position: relative;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 24px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4));
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .crystal svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .crystal .shine { animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.85; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
        }
        h1 {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2rem);
            color: var(--amethyst-glow);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.25);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.75rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }
        .bar-wrap {
            height: 8px;
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .bar {
            height: 100%;
            width: 35%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--amethyst), var(--amethyst-glow));
            border-radius: 4px;
            animation: loading 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes loading {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
            50% { transform: translateX(200%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="crystal" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <defs>
                    <linearGradient id="crystal-grad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                        <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#a78bfa"/>
                        <stop offset="50%" style="stop-color:#7c3aed"/>
                        <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#5b21b6"/>
                    </linearGradient>
                    <linearGradient id="crystal-shine" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                        <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)"/>
                        <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:rgba(255,255,255,0)"/>
                    </linearGradient>
                </defs>
                <path d="M32 4 L56 32 L32 60 L8 32 Z" fill="url(#crystal-grad)" class="shine"/>
                <path d="M32 4 L56 32 L32 60 L8 32 Z" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.2)" stroke-width="1" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Amethyste Idle</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">RPG • Idle • Navigateur</p>
        <div class="card">
            <p><strong>Maintenance en cours</strong></p>
            <p class="message">Nous améliorons l’aventure. Revenez dans quelques instants.</p>
            <div class="bar-wrap">
                <div class="bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="33" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="footer">Merci de votre patience, aventurier.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
